{"tid":2396803,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登稱害怕川普洩密 不應讓其再收到機密資訊簡報","createTime":"2021-02-06T02:02:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T03:12:17.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a056579eebf37088953393a621734dd40017db20","tid":2396803,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"美國卸任總統依照慣例可在下台後繼續接獲機密情資簡報，不過這項慣例可能不適用於前總統川普身上。現任總統拜登（Joe Biden）周五（2/5）受訪時表示，他認為不應該讓川普繼續收到簡報。<br />\n<br />\n拜登接受哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）節目主持人專訪時，被問及是否擔心川普將繼續收到機密情報時，他回說：「我只是覺得，他沒有必要收到情資簡報。繼續給他簡報有何好處？他知道這些會有什麼狀況？除了可能說溜嘴之外。」<br />\n<br />\n根據美聯社報導，是否繼續讓卸任總統獲得情資簡報，決定權握在現任政府手上。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n她寫著：「川普與外國實體有著相當大的商業糾葛。這些商業關係對其他國家的情報單位來說，是容易滲透的弱點。」<br />\n<br />\n據報導，川普企業目前債台高築，債款金額高達4億美元（約112億元台幣）<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210206/KDI7C2R3S5D2DGWWWW7UBUW7VI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FKDI7C2R3S5D2DGWWWW7UBUW7VI%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=f6c3b12f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210206%2FKDI7C2R3S5D2DGWWWW7UBUW7VI%2F&h=dd87647b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210206/KDI7C2R3S5D2DGWWWW7UBUW7VI/</a>"},{"pid":"40eb133fc869a89bb39725920d48b08f9a51524e","tid":2396803,"uid":60977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"軍部唔buy燈燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47c613a365a2c05a614dbd3c76d1e690a58c8f6","tid":2396803,"uid":23058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:05:45.000Z","msg":"4億債對大企業 算啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9164d98242d90d856feb0bb9fa36c25429f837","tid":2396803,"uid":83713,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-